title: Radiohead / On A Friday Demos 1986-91
description:
Radiohead/On A Friday - Demo Tapes 1986-1991 (Remastered) (Size: 395.5 MB)
 	
A collection of the Radiohead/On A Friday/Shindig demo tapes with some slight remastering although the quality is quite hissy in places. These are encoded to lossy 320kb/ps MP3 for ease of sharing from the original FLAC files.

The tapes included are the:
1986 On A Friday Demo (Abingdon Music Room) - 5 Track
1988 Woodworm Studios Demo - 3 Track
1990 Shindig Demo - 15 Track
1990 Union Street Demo - 14 Track
1991 On A Friday Demo - 3 Track
1991 Manic Hedgehog Demo - 5 Track
